---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import "../styles/global.css";
---

<Layout
	title="About | 10 Billion Travelers"
	description="Meet Kevin White — over 1 million miles traveled across 26 countries. Learn the story behind 10 Billion Travelers."
>
	<!-- Page Header -->
	<section class="page-header">
		<div class="container">
			<h1>Our Story</h1>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Bio Section -->
	<section class="bio-section">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="bio-grid">
				<div class="bio-image-wrap">
					<div class="bio-image-placeholder" aria-label="Kevin White portrait">
						<span>Kevin White</span>
					</div>
					<p class="image-caption">Having fun on the Great Wall</p>
				</div>
				<div class="bio-content">
					<p class="bio-lead">"I was born to travel! I've logged over 1 million miles. Before I'm 100 years old there will be 10 Billion people alive. I'll inspire as many travelers as possible!"</p>

					<p>I was born into a modest family in Western North Carolina. Travel outside of North Carolina was minimal. When I did travel, it was only to South Carolina and Virginia. Travel outside the US&mdash;forget about it! That was for the privileged.</p>

					<p>I didn't receive my first passport until I was 30 years old. I have now logged over 1 million miles and traveled to 26 different countries. That's not 26 trips to the Bahamas. I have been to many of the major destinations and I have also gone off the beaten path to places most people don't even know exist.</p>

					<p>I have traveled enough to know the inner workings of airlines, hotels, restaurants, and attractions. I look forward to sharing all of this with you through our Vlogs, Blogs, Reviews, and Travel Services. Your new experience begins now!</p>

					<p class="bio-author">Kevin White</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- CTA -->
	<section class="cta-section">
		<div class="container">
			<h2>Have a Question?</h2>
			<p class="cta-sub">We'd Love to Hear From You</p>
			<a href="/contact/" class="btn">Email Us</a>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>

<style>
	.page-header {
		background: var(--color-white);
		padding: 60px 0;
		text-align: center;
		border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
	}
	.page-header h1 {
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 2px;
	}

	.bio-section {
		padding: 60px 0;
	}
	.bio-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 300px 1fr;
		gap: 48px;
		align-items: start;
	}
	.bio-image-placeholder {
		width: 283px;
		height: 300px;
		background: var(--color-bg-light);
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
		color: var(--color-text-secondary);
		font-style: italic;
		font-size: 14px;
	}
	.image-caption {
		font-size: 13px;
		color: var(--color-text-secondary);
		text-align: center;
		margin-top: 8px;
		font-style: italic;
	}
	.bio-lead {
		font-size: 18px;
		font-weight: 700;
		color: var(--color-heading);
		font-family: var(--font-heading);
		line-height: 1.5;
		margin-bottom: 24px;
	}
	.bio-content p {
		margin-bottom: 16px;
		line-height: 1.7;
	}
	.bio-author {
		font-family: var(--font-heading);
		font-weight: 600;
		font-size: 16px;
		color: var(--color-heading);
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 1px;
		margin-top: 24px;
	}

	.cta-section {
		padding: 80px 0;
		text-align: center;
		background: var(--color-white);
	}
	.cta-section h2 {
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 2px;
		margin-bottom: 8px;
	}
	.cta-sub {
		font-size: 17px;
		color: var(--color-text-secondary);
		margin-bottom: 32px;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 1px;
		font-size: 14px;
	}

	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.bio-grid {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
			gap: 32px;
		}
		.bio-image-placeholder {
			width: 100%;
			max-width: 283px;
			margin: 0 auto;
		}
	}
</style>
